overview: Heather (Skye Blue) might seem to be nothing more than a hot blonde influencer who loves the finer things in life, but she's actually the leader of a team of sexy jet-setting con artists (Jenna Starr, Zoey Sinn and Alexis Tae), who take rich guys for everything they've got, and she's got her sights set on a new mark, Brent (Scott Nails). But when Brent's wife, former con artist-turned-businesswoman Maxine (Cherie DeVille), finds out some little blonde upstart is targeting her man—and her private jet—this might mean war...
title: Jet Setters
